    <note>Zhao(1) Zicheng [17675] Zhao(1) Xiaozong's [9011] natural father, he chose to follow a civil career rather than enter the imperial palace after the future Xiaozong was adopted as heir of Gaozong. He was enfeoffed as the Xiu Wang, a title inherited by his eldest son, Bogui [17676], and then by Bogui's son #9, Shimi(2) [17683]. Shimi's elder brother (Bogui's son #8) was in charge of the Xiu Wang ancestral temple in 1221. SS(PRC), 222.6410. CBD, 4, 3382.</note>
